data.description: Charming 2 Bedroom 2 Bath country home offers the perfect combination of comfort and convenience. Includes a 16 x 24' detached garage and a 14 x 40' RV/Shop (with 50-amp Service) located in the highly sought after W Highland Drive area. Need room for horses? This mostly Timbered 10 acre property is ready to welcome you home. Have your morning coffee, afternoon sun tea, or evening bbq with friends 'al fresco' style on this beautiful wrap around deck! Enjoy the Idaho outdoors in your own backyard retreat - can you smell the Pine and Cedar Trees yet? Property may be sub-dividable: add a second home? (check local zoning - easements are in place). Location, Location, Location: Situated near the heart of Coeur d'Alene, this home offers the best of both worlds - a peaceful suburban setting while being just minutes away from the downtown attractions, schools, parks, shopping, water sports, hiking, biking, and all the recreational opportunities North Idaho and the CdA Lake have to offer.
